    <item>
      <title>押注美联储更积极降息，日元升值超过 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/yen-gains-more-than-1-on-bets-of-more-aggressive-fed-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员加大对美联储在 2024 年更大幅度降息的押注，以及对日本央行退出负利率的猜测挥之不去，日元兑美元汇率上涨逾 1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/yen-gains-more-than-1-on-bets-of-more-aggressive-fed-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 03:46:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储后美元回落，股票和债券上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储暗示明年降息后，股市和债券上涨，随着通胀缓解，重新点燃了整个市场的看涨脉搏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 23:40:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国库存减少后油价从六月以来的最低水平上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-14</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于积极的需求信号，包括美国库存下降以及美联储准备降息的迹象，油价从五个月低点上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-14</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 23:40:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析师：美联储引发的亚洲股市反弹有望延续至 2024 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/investors-see-asian-stocks-bonds-and-currencies-boosted-by-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，继美联储发出明年降息信号后，亚洲市场的跨资产上涨可能会持续到 2024 年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/investors-see-asian-stocks-bonds-and-currencies-boosted-by-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 22:41:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
